extracted.bw-session__description: Heal your body from the inside out with the traditional Bikram Yoga Hot 26+2 class, the original hot yoga series. A non-vinyasa and static based set sequence practiced in a heated room focused on increasing the flexibility of the spine and improving the overall health of the body and mind. Room temp is 105 degrees. All levels welcome

9:00 AM – 10:00 AM PST
        
        
          
          View details

extracted.bw-session__description: A dynamic practice focused on moving the body along with the breath.  Sequencing of each class is unique to each class/teacher. Some preparations for inversions and Level 2 postures may be introduced, with options for Level 1 students to ease the transition from Level 1 to Level 2 classes. Be prepared to sweat and move. The room temp is 95 degrees. Suitable for students with some yoga experience looking to have an invigorating and dynamic experience.
